Joe Spano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Spano 0 Joseph Peter Spano (born July 7, 1946) is an American actor who was originally best known for his role as Lt. Henry Goldblume on Hill Street Blues. Spano is now best known for his work on NCIS as FBI Special Agent Tobias C. Fornell.
